actions.instruction: Head east on Wilhelm-Fay-Straße. Go for 797 m.
Turn right onto Westerbachstraße (L3440). Go for 419 m.
Turn left and take ramp onto A648 (Wiesbadener Straße) toward Wiesbaden/A66/Frankfurt-Miquelallee. Go for 2.4 km.
Continue on A66. Go for 19.4 km.
Take exit 7 toward Wiesbaden-Nordenstadt/Wiesbaden-Delkenheim/Hochheim/WI-Erbenheim/Gewerbegebiet I/Daimlerring/Siemensstraße/Hochheim a.M./WI-Delkenheim. Go for 240 m.
Turn slightly left onto Borsigstraße. Go for 483 m.
Turn right onto Otto-von-Guericke-Ring. Go for 154 m.
Continue on Daimlerring. Go for 217 m.
Take the 2nd exit from roundabout onto Hessenring. Go for 91 m.
Arrive at Hessenring. Your destination is on the right.
